  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3 partial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level is set at 3. Ten of thirteen credibility factors are assessed; three factors (Use error, Model inputs, Equivalency of input parameters) are marked not-assessed on the basis that they fall 'beyond the current project scope', without concrete justification for why that scope boundary is acceptable at MRL 3. Decision is recorded as Accepted despite the unassessed factors.",
